text: Sonie Rajbhandari () born in Kathmandu, Nepal is a Nepali Model and the title winner of Miss Nepal International 2014. She has also represented Nepal in Miss International beauty pageant which was held in Japan. ==References== Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:People from Kathmandu Category:Nepalese models Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
